‚ö†Ô∏è Important Notes
- You don‚Äôt need to recreate the subnet or move instances‚Äîjust update the route table and IP settings.
- If you're using a NAT Gateway, remove its route from the subnet‚Äôs route table to avoid conflicts.
- EC2 instances in the subnet will need public IPs to be reachable from the internet.
